-- BoCom expects slight rise in bad loans over the next year
-- By Engen Tham
-- Thu Aug 21, 2014 05:58AM EDT
-- None



SHANGHAI, Aug 21 (Reuters) - China's Bank of Communications <601328.SS> <3328.HK> expects to see a slight rise in non-performing loans over the next year, its Chief Risk Officer Yang Dongping said on Thursday, adding that the overall risk was "manageable".

